{"tid":947603,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"淺談一下 我鍾意睇av之後神奇既變化","createTime":"2018-12-19T11:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T12:29:30.000Z","uid":138138,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ba55df612e422e9c7f4c23ca4125913c26853bf","tid":947603,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"先至聲明 我開呢個post絕對唔係為左哂命同自戀<br />\n光陰似箭 我鐘意睇av已經差不多一年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 鍾意av之前 我人生冇咩目標 個樣都唔係幾靚仔<br />\n所以自信心特別低 成日都比同學蝦<br />\n<br />\n至從留意左av之後 成個人精神哂 自信都開始黎番<br />\nav真係影視界華陀<br />\n<br />\n半年之後 因為睇左清水健 嘅打飛機教學(特別係用手 )<br />\n我都開始自己劣下 我自己都劣得愈來愈好 <br />\n我開始有朋友 連以前蝦我既蛋散 反而係我蝦返佢"},{"pid":"2851ff3340ebd46bcaef3480737c6b6068261079","tid":947603,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:39:31.000Z","msg":"睇精神科啦"},{"pid":"f10a12e6ddb92222df5569effe9707851e99106f","tid":947603,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"你點恰佢？劣返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"d2828fb177370da7172952b454b253a3a9ba6df5","tid":947603,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2851ff3340ebd46bcaef3480737c6b6068261079","tid":947603,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:39:31.000Z","msg":"睇精神科啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"我個人好精神"},{"pid":"9a678f8890d0f25e000235f392ce050da0cc979e","tid":947603,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f10a12e6ddb92222df5569effe9707851e99106f","tid":947603,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"你點恰佢？劣返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T11:46:17.000Z","msg":"劣佢j =益左佢<br />\n所以而家我逼佢幫我劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f3e3983d5cef91fa6d31fc912b89ab50816734","tid":947603,"uid":38904,"l